HOW TO USE
==========

- First Step:

python expid.py -h

python expid.py --new ecearth --HPC ithaca --description "stress test experiment"

Let us suppose "i00f" is the new expid created in resultant of above command

- Second Step:

vi /cfu/autosubmit/i00f/conf/expdef_i00f.conf
vi /cfu/autosubmit/i00f/conf/autosubmit_i00f.conf

- Third Step:

python create_exp.py i00f

- Fourth Step:

nohup python autosubmit.py i00f >& i00f_01.log &


